query:
SELECT
                p.id as probe_id,
                p.http_method,
                p.request_path,
                p.request_body,
                d.alias,
                d.type as model_type,
                ak.secret as system_api_key
            FROM probes p
            JOIN deployed_models d ON p.deployment_id = d.id
            CROSS JOIN api_keys ak
            WHERE p.id = $1 AND ak.id = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'::uuid
